                                    ExecAsUser: 1b,
                                    Cmd: "tag @s add quest_assist_cull_done"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "COMMAND",
                                    Cmd: "title @p actionbar [{\"text\":\"Field cull logged. Grant work: one of three ledgers closed.\",\"color\":\"yellow\"}]"
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Conditions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "HAS_ITEM_IN_INVENTORY",
                                    Operation: "EQUALS",
                                    Item: "minecraft:bone",
                                    Quantity: 8
                                },
                                {
                                    Type: "PLAYER_TAG",
                                    Operation: "NOT_EQUALS",
                                    Name: "quest_assist_cull_done"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "bone_button"
                        },
                        {
                            Name: "I will be back after dark",
                            Actions: [
                                {
                                    Type: "CLOSE_DIALOG"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "later_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "I run fieldwork for the lab. Ran. The grant was consolidated for verification and the verification never came back, so now I count moths from my kitchen window. The night surveys on Blossom Path are ruined — shamblers and archers trample every plot after dark. Cull eight of either and bring me proof. The field pays by the specimen, out of a budget line nobody has verified yet."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Blossom Path after dark is honest work and honest risk — go only if your team is ready, and come home if it is not. Eight pieces of rotten flesh or eight bones is proof enough for the ledger. Miri handles collections by the shore and Raan does geology up the lane, if daylight suits you better."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Kofi — fieldwork brief",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
        },
